4=Blue    5=Magenta 6=Cyan    7=White
8=Bright Black (Dark Gray)
9=Bright Red          A=Bright Green
B=Bright Yellow       C=Bright Blue
D=Bright Magenta      E=Bright Cyan
F=Bright White

